article.description: — Anthony Roberts had 20 points as Stony Brook beat Bryant 86-78 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Roberts scores 20 to carry Stony Brook over Bryant 86-78
article.linkText: Roberts scores 20 to carry Stony Brook over Bryant 86-78
article.story: STONY BROOK, N.Y. -- — Anthony Roberts had 20 points as Stony Brook beat Bryant 86-78 on Saturday night. Tykei Greene had 19 points and eight rebounds for Stony Brook (5-4). Jahlil Jenkins added 13 points. Omar Habwe had 12 points. Charles Pride scored a season-high 27 points for the Bulldogs (4-7). Greg Calixte added 12 points and 13 rebounds. Adham Eleeda had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
